Vor fi ele destul de atractive afiliatilor comparandu-le cu cele ale competitiei. Cum sa-i atrag pe afliliati ca sa se alature?

Post Afiliere Xpress se face intr-un mod in care se poate lucra cu configuratia implicita
Cu toate acestea, ar trebui sa verificati configuratia si sa gasiti aplicatiile pentru nevoile dumneavoastra..

Descrierea detaliata a tuturor optiunilor de configurare poate fi gasita in ghidul utilizatorului de cunostinte

O campanie implicita este creata in timpul instalarii. Puteti sa o modificati pentru a crea propriile campanii

. Campaniile sunt utilizate pentru a grupa un set de produse (sau doar un singur produs), care au aceleaĹźi setÄri

. De exemplu, puteĹŁi avea campania pentru produsul 1, unde veti recompensa afiliaĹŁii dumneavoastrÄ pe clic Ĺźi o altÄ campanie pentru produsul 2, Ă®n cazul Ă®n care afiliatii primesc comisioane pe vĂ˘nzare

. Sau puteĹŁi avea campanie cu produse low cost, care va avea 40% pe comisioanele de vĂ˘nzare Ĺźi o altÄ campanie cu produse scumpe cu 15% pe comision de vĂ˘nzare.

Ar trebui sa setezi functionalitatea email-ului. Aceasta include:
  • - cum sunt email-urile trimise. Puteti opta fie pentru functia mail () sau serverul SMTP.
  • Sabloanele email-urilor - acestea sunt sabloanele care sunt folosite atunci cand sistemul trimite automat email-uri, dupa inscriere sau dupa notificarile de vanzare
  • Notificarile de e-mail - puteti configura ce fel de notificari sa primti ca si comerciant si ce notificari vor fi disponibile pentru afiliati. Asigurati-va ca email-ul este configurat corect - incercati sa trimiteti e-mailuri de testare. Fara email-urile de lucru afiliatii nu vor primi confirmarea despre inscrierea lor. etc

source:
Integration is a way to connect the affiliate system to your current website, shopping cart or payment gateway in a way that affiliate system will be notified about referrals and purchases.
When notified, affiliate system registers the sale, finds referring affiliate (if any) and creates appropriate commission for him.

Integration usually means adding few lines of code into your pages, and it is described step-by-step in the Integration guide for most common shopping carts and payment systems.%s
translation:
Integrarea este o modalitate de a conecta sistemul de afiliat la site-ul dvs. curent, cosul de cumparaturi sau sistemul de plati gateway-ul intr-un mod in care sistemul de afiliere va notifica recomandarile si achizitiile.
Atunci cand este notificat, sistemul de afiliat inregistreza vanzararile, constata trimitere afiliat (daca exista) si creeaza comisioane adecvate pentru ei

. Integrarea inseamna de obicei, adaugarea catorva linii de cod in paginile dvs. si este descrisa pas-cu-pas in ghidul de integrare pentru cele mai comune cumparaturi online si sisteme de plati.%s

source:
When you have configured your campaigns, defined correct commissions, and created some banners/links, you should test the system.
The best is to simulate the whole process from affiliate’s and your point of view:
  1. Sign up as some testing affiliate – after approval you should receive confirmation email with your password, and you should be able to log in to your affiliate panel
  2. Log in to affiliates panel, get the code for banners/links and put them onto some testing page
  3. Click on the banner and check that the click is registered
  4. After the click, try to make test sale and check that sale commission was registered in affiliate system (only for per sale or per lead commissions)
If you experience some problems in any of these steps, turn on Debug event logging and look at Troubleshooting%s
translation:
Cand v-ati configurat campaniile dvs., ati definit comisioanele corect si ati creat unele bannere / link-uri, ar trebui sa testati sistemul.
Cel mai bine este sa simulati intregul proces al afiliat si din punctul dumneavoastra de vedere:
  1. Inscrie-ti unii afiliati de testare - dupa aprobare ar trebui sa primiti e-mail de confirmare cu parola si ar trebui sa va puteti conecta la panoul afiliat
  2. Conectati-va la panoul de afiliere, pentru a primi coduri pentru bannere / link-uri si puneti-le pe unele pagini de testare
  3. Faceti clic pe banner si verificati daca clicul este inregistrat
  4. Dupa clic, incercati sa faceti testul de vanzare si sa verificati daca comisioanele de vanzare au fost inregistrate in sistemul de afiliere (numai pe vanzari sau pe comenziile comisioanelor)
Daca va confruntati cu unele probleme, in oricare dintre aceste etape, porniti jurnalul evenimentelor de depanare si uitati-va la depanare%s

Dupa ce au testat cu succes integrarea sistemului de afiliere cu site-ul dvs., totul este gata pentru a porni programul de promovare a noului afiliat, astfel incat veti atrage afiliati noi sa vi se alature

. Este o necesitate de a pune link-ul la informatiile programului de afiliere sau o inscriere formularul pe site-ul tau. Numeste link-ul ca program de afiliere, webmasteri face bani, Afiliatii etc Acest lucru va atrage vizitatorii catre site-ul dvs. si se pot converti la afiliati dumneavoastra

. Pentru a atinge mai mult potential, prezentati programul dvs. directoarelor afiliate. Exista zeci de directoare afiliate pe web, vizitate de mii de afiliatii cu experienta in fiecare zi.

translation: Raportul lunar cu statistici si vanzari este trimis in fiecare luna. Este in ziua specificata in "raport trimis la " si contine date din luna precedenta. Ex. translation:
Modul GeoIP Core va traduce în fiecare adresa IP Locatie (ţară, oraş, latitudine şi longitudine).
Toata funcţionalitatea GeoIP alt se bazează pe acest plugin.
Daca acest plugin nu va fi activat, alte plugin-uri GeoIP nu vor funcţiona.

source:
GeoIp plugin is based on free GeoIp database offered by MaxMind.
Plugin requires GeoIp binary database (filename GeoLiteCity.dat) saved in your plugin directory (server/plugins/GeoIp/).
You can downlaod latest version of GeoIp database from here: %s.
(Don't forget to extract downloaded file before copying to plugin directory)
Free GeoIp database has lower accuracy as paid version offered by MaxMind, but for most of installations it will be enough, because in most cases you are interested in country level information and City level is not so important.
If you want to have more accurate results of IP identification, you will need to buy GeoCity library from %s and replace file GeoLiteCity.dat in your plugin directory with one you received from MaxMind.
Accuracy of Free GeoIp database: Over 99.3%% on a country level and 76%% on a city level for the US within a 25 mile radius.
Accuracy of Paid GeoIp database: Over 99.8%% on a country level and 81%% on a city level for the US within a 25 mile radius.
translation:
GeoIp plugin are ca temelie baza de date GeoIp oferita de MaxMind.
Cererile de plugin GeoIp a bazei de date binare (filename GeoLiteCity.dat) salvat in directorul plugin (server/plugins/GeoIp/).
Puteti download ultima versiune a bazei de date GeoIp de aici: %s.
(Nu uitati sa extrageti fisierele downlodate inainte sa le copiati in directorul plugin)
Baza de date gratuita GeoIp are o precizie mai mica decat cea contra cost oferita de MaxMind,insa pentru majoritatea instalarilor va fi destul, deoarece in majoritatea cazurilor sunteti interesati de informatiile de nivel a tarilor, iar nivelele de oras sunt mai putin importante.
daca doriti sa aveti rezultate mai precise a identificatorilor IP, va trebui sa cumparati cartile GeoCity de la %s si sa schimbati fisierul GeoLiteCity.dat in directorul plugin-ului dvs. director primit de la MaxMind.
Precizia bazei de date Free GeoIp : Mai mare de 99.3%% pentru un nivel al tarii si 76%% pentru un nivel al orasului in limita radiusului de 25 mile.
Precizia bazei de date Platite GeoIp : Over 99.8%% pentru un nivel al tarii si 81%% pentru un nivel al orasului in limita radiusului de 25 mile.

source: This is a formula based on which all the commissions will be counted. In case you want to payout flat commission, the formula requires only numbers: 3-4-5. This structure defines tiers from right to left, meaning the first one from left is top tier, then their child, then grandchild etc...
translation: This is a formula based on which all the commissions will be counted. If main commission structure should be set to 1st tier 5%; 2nd tier 4% and 3rd tier 3% the formula would look like %3-%4-%5. In case you want to payout flat commission, the formula requires only numbers: 3-4-5. This structure defines tiers from right to left, meaning the first one from left is top tier, then their child, then grandchild etc...

source:
If main commission structure should be set to 1st tier 5%; 2nd tier 4% and 3rd tier 3% the formula would look like %3-%4-%5. In case you want to payout flat commission, the formula requires only numbers: 3-4-5. This structure defines tiers from right to left, meaning the first one from left is top tier, then their child, then grandchild etc... The missing tier commission always goes to the parent affiliate (from right to left).

E.g. in case of five levels %2-%2-%2-%4-%5 the commission structure changes like this, if the last affiliate is missing:
All 5 tiers: %2-%2-%2-%4-%5
4 tiers: %2-%2-%2-%9
3 tiers: %2-%2-%11
2 tiers: %2-%13
1 tier: %15
translation:
If main commission structure should be set to 1st tier 5%; 2nd tier 4% and 3rd tier 3% the formula would look like %3-%4-%5. In case you want to payout flat commission, the formula requires only numbers: 3-4-5. This structure defines tiers from right to left, meaning the first one from left is top tier, then their child, then grandchild etc... The missing tier commission always goes to the parent affiliate (from right to left).

E.g. in case of five levels %2-%2-%2-%4-%5 the commission structure changes like this, if the last affiliate is missing:
All 5 tiers: %2-%2-%2-%4-%5
4 tiers: %2-%2-%2-%9
3 tiers: %2-%2-%11
2 tiers: %2-%13
1 tier: %15

source:
The last affiliate tier with no parent in a sale will get the commission as a difference between the totalcost and the sum of commissions given to lower tiers.
Notice: Use this plugin only in case you want to pay all the totalcost (100% commission) to your affiliates.
translation:
The last affiliate tier with no parent in a sale will get the commission as a difference between the totalcost and the sum of commissions given to lower tiers.
Notice: Use this plugin only in case you want to pay all the totalcost (100% commission) to your affiliates.

source:
Example 1:
Let's have the main commission structure set like this: 1st tier 50%; 2nd tier 30% and 3rd tier 20%. Now here are some cases:
  • Commission for all 3 tiers: Every tier gets the commission noramlly (50%, 30%, 20%)
  • Commission for 2 tiers: The 1st tier gets 50% and the 2nd tier gets 'totalcost' - 50%(lower tiers)
  • Commission for 1 tier: The 1st tier gets commission of 'totalcost' - 0(there is no lower tier) = 100%
Example 2:
Let's have the main commission structure set like this: 1st tier 30%; 2nd tier 20% and 3rd tier 10%, for all tiers the commission is 60%. Now here are some cases:
  • Commission for all 3 tiers: Every tier gets the commission noramlly (30%, 20%, 10%)
  • Commission for 2 tiers: The 1st tier gets 30% and the 2nd tier gets 'totalcost' - 30%(lower tiers) = 70%, for all tiers the commission is 100%!
  • Commission for 1 tier: The 1st tier gets commission of 'totalcost' - 0(there is no lower tier), so for all tiers the commission is 100%!
translation:
Example 1:
Let's have the main commission structure set like this: 1st tier 50%; 2nd tier 30% and 3rd tier 20%. Now here are some cases:
  • Commission for all 3 tiers: Every tier gets the commission noramlly (50%, 30%, 20%)
  • Commission for 2 tiers: The 1st tier gets 50% and the 2nd tier gets 'totalcost' - 50%(lower tiers)
  • Commission for 1 tier: The 1st tier gets commission of 'totalcost' - 0(there is no lower tier) = 100%
Example 2:
Let's have the main commission structure set like this: 1st tier 30%; 2nd tier 20% and 3rd tier 10%, for all tiers the commission is 60%. Now here are some cases:
  • Commission for all 3 tiers: Every tier gets the commission noramlly (30%, 20%, 10%)
  • Commission for 2 tiers: The 1st tier gets 30% and the 2nd tier gets 'totalcost' - 30%(lower tiers) = 70%, for all tiers the commission is 100%!
  • Commission for 1 tier: The 1st tier gets commission of 'totalcost' - 0(there is no lower tier), so for all tiers the commission is 100%!
